* List of potential duplicate runners
* Purpose:          Identifies runners with the same First Name, Last Name, and Birthdate.
* Why Birthdate:    Included to distinguish between family members (e.g., Father/Son) 
*                    who share the same name but have different birth years.
* When to use:      After importing data or during the final registration audit.
* How it works:     Scans for matches across all three fields and opens a Browse screen.
* Double-click any entry to resolve the duplication.
*
Remove Duplicates   Browse
Field               LAST NAME
Field               FIRST NAME
Field               BIRTHDATE